subsection.p:
(30)
i. small clauses (causatives and complements of perception verbs);
ii. non-finite clauses (including both to-infinitives and small clauses);
iii. non-indicative clauses (including subjunctive tensed clauses and non-finite clauses).

(31)
i. small clauses (causatives and complements of perception verbs, except for the object argument of the lower verb);
ii. non-finite clauses (including both to-infinitives and small clauses).
